{"tid":1135714,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"告別平成時代惹眾怒！Sana遭南韓網友砲轟：「不看眼色」","createTime":"2019-05-02T13:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T13:28:18.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f562a0b29c631c32a1bd258cd6ecf23b21279deb","tid":1135714,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T13:10:54.000Z","msg":"在全球矚目下，日本明仁天皇於4月30日退位，結束30年平成時代，今（1）日德仁天皇繼位，開啟嶄新的令和元年。南韓女團TWICE有3位日本籍成員，其中一位日籍團員Sana在官方IG發文告別平成時代，怎料該篇文章卻引起南韓網友的怒火。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/05/01/1903565-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F05%2F01%2F1903565-XXL.jpg&h=c6fb4702&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲Sana發文告別平成時代，惹怒南韓網友。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/05/01/1903564-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F05%2F01%2F1903564-XXL.jpg&h=5d5e0b6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n30日Sana用母語在TWICE官方IG發文寫道：「作為平成年代出生的人，面對平成的結束總感覺有些寂寞，但平成辛苦了！讓我們朝著令和新時代出發，愉快地度過平成最後一天吧！」文末還標記著「謝謝平成」、「令和請多指教」的hashtag。怎料Sana單純的心情抒發，卻引起南韓網友不滿，認為了解南韓歷史的民眾應該都知道日本天皇代表什麼，還砲轟經紀公司JYP沒有制止成員發表敏感議題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/05/01/1903550-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F05%2F01%2F1903550-XXL.jpg&h=e3925cdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲Sana用母語發文紀念令和時代來臨。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2626292/org/987386eb340c66903f301879a7b42015.jpg/_TbrVytjF68UsoO17XF-9ehYE4pbzHtVQpFWHUKRVh0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2626292%2Forg%2F987386eb340c66903f301879a7b42015.jpg%2F_TbrVytjF68UsoO17XF-9ehYE4pbzHtVQpFWHUKRVh0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ae6427b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網友更指出，過去成員多賢穿著慰安婦應援T恤時，官方為了避免爭議而刪除，但這次Sana祝賀日本天皇的貼文卻被保留，更表示TWICE的韓國籍成員在光復節時考慮到有日本成員在隊內，因此不曾發表有關節日的紀念文，如今Sana此舉惹怒南韓網友，不少人直接留言砲轟：「失望了，雖然看著韓國活動的日本人不該考慮什麼歷史問題，但還是稍微有點眼色吧」、「請慢慢的消息吧。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/05/01/1903583-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F05%2F01%2F1903583-XXL.jpg&h=d320ee52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲南韓網友狂砲轟Sana。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/05/01/1903582-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F05%2F01%2F1903582-XXL.jpg&h=4885a23d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過也有理性網友出面緩頰，認為此事Sana只是以作為一個日本人的心情，感嘆世代的交替並沒有其它意思，更表示留言怒罵的網友情緒過於激動，有中立網友留言：「其實sana說的話沒問題，只是感慨一下平成年成為過去式」、「梅西那顆自由球是救不到的。」「不是啊！難道這不只是在說2018結束啦，我們一起度過充實美滿的2019吧，只是這樣的感慨評論而已不是嗎？」"},{"pid":"1c6fea1c127fb223451f2d65e71b4c7b9ae94940","tid":1135714,"uid":138138,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T13:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i1evgVp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi1evgVp.jpg&h=959fc5d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"535810e8ae0e2c4fec140c891d86302794107b07","tid":1135714,"uid":10313,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T13:18:42.000Z","msg":"梅西那顆自由球是救不到的。"},{"pid":"4b68ca6e84606c4c31338ec4e9f0cf7beb1fd474","tid":1135714,"uid":187264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T13:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SYNAs25.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSYNAs25.png&h=e356460e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6e61a4116e9f03afb939cc3462e94944058af86","tid":1135714,"uid":67551,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T13:28:18.000Z","msg":"中國韓國都係一樣戇鳩鳩"}]}